kiśora	dear boy
na:-tava dāsī:-	we (are) Thy servants
avaśī-karoṣi kim	teasing us why
pradiśa-ambaram-	give the clothes
ambujekṣaṇa-	O Lotus eyed one!
iti-udita:-	thus being told
tvaṃ smitam-eva	Thou smile only
